      <title>由于中国复苏和美联储宽松，亚洲股市将于 2024 年击败美国股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/asian-stocks-seen-beating-us-peers-in-2024-on-china-revival-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储可能降息削弱美元以及投资者对中国廉价股票的信心改善，亚洲股市今年的表现将优于美国股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/asian-stocks-seen-beating-us-peers-in-2024-on-china-revival-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
