      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 14:19:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德、方舟文件修正案最终推动比特币 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/blackrock-ark-file-amended-forms-in-final-push-for-bitcoin-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BlackRock Inc.、Ark 和其他几家在美国直接投资比特币的交易所交易基金的潜在发行人周一向美国证券交易委员会提交了修改后的申请表格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/blackrock-ark-file-amended-forms-in-final-push-for-bitcoin-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 12:08:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美元贬值，墨西哥比索与新兴货币同行一起上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/emerging-market-assets-fall-in-step-with-global-flight-from-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥比索周一触及四个多月以来的最高水平，与大多数新兴市场货币一起上涨。交易员正在等待本周美国关键通胀数据的解读，因为人们对美联储何时开始降息的押注不断变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/emerging-market-assets-fall-in-step-with-global-flight-from-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 12:08:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
